- Private API doc access token tu Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}.
- Auth refresh/logout doc refresh token tu cookie, khong doc tu body.
- Collection nay duoc tao tu code route/validator/controller hien tai, khong dua tren tri nho hay tai lieu cu.

